# Code Quality Standards

Always:

- Strong typing
- Reusable components
- Clean architecture
- Modular code

Never:

- Any types
- Inline hacks
- Duplicate code

Files should remain:

- Readable
- Maintainable
- Scalable

Use descriptive naming.

Prefer composition over complexity.
